Description: A tool for the gamemaster of a tabletop rpg session.
 The "GM-Companion" is a tool for the gamemaster of a tabletop rpg session.
 .
 .
 Features:
 .
 - Playing music and sounds according to the situation
 . 
 - Playing music from a webradio
 .
 - Dice rolling
 .
 - Combat Tracker
 .
 - Name Generator
 .
 - Character Overview
 .
 - Map viewer
 .
 - Unit conversion
 .
 - Notes
